Aşağıdaki devirli ondalık sayılar olan $0.\dot{3}$, $0.\dot{2}\dot{4}$ ve $42.34\dot{7}\dot{8}$ kesirlere çevrilmiştir.
\vspace{-1em}
\begin{small}
\begin{centerpage}{0.9\textwidth}
\begin{align*}
\text{İlk olarak \qquad}0.\dot{3} &= 0,3333 \ldots \\
0.\dot{3} \times 10 &= 0,333 \ldots \times 10 &= 3,333 \ldots\\
0.\dot{3} \times 1 &= 0,333 \ldots \times 1 &= 0,333 \ldots\\[-1em]\cline{1-2}
\text{çıkararak, }0.\dot{3} \times 10 - 0.\dot{3} \times 1 &=3\\
0.\dot{3} \times (10-1) &= 3\\
0.\dot{3} \times 9&=3\\
\therefore 0.\dot{3}&=\dfrac{3}{9}=\dfrac{1}{3}
\end{align*}
\end{centerpage}
\begin{centerpage}{0.9\textwidth}
\begin{align*}
\text{Şimdi \qquad}0.\dot{2}\dot{4}&=\phantom{0}0,24242424 \ldots\\
0.\dot{2}\dot{4} \times 100 &= 0,242424 \ldots \times 100 &= 24,24242424 \ldots\\
0.\dot{2}\dot{4} \times 1 &= 0,242424 \ldots \times 1 &= \phantom{0}0,24242424 \ldots\\[-1em]\cline{1-2}
\text{çıkararak, }0.\dot{2}\dot{4} \times 99 &=24\\
\therefore 0.\dot{2}\dot{4}&=\dfrac{24}{99} =\dfrac{8}{33}
\end{align*}
\end{centerpage}
\begin{centerpage}{0.9\textwidth}
‌\begin{align*}
\text{Son olarak \qquad}42.34\dot{7}\dot{8}&=\phantom{0000}42,34787878 \ldots\\
42.34\dot{7}\dot{8} \times 10000 &= 42,34787878 \ldots \times 10000 &= 423478,78787878 \ldots\\
42.34\dot{7}\dot{8} \times 100 &= 42,347878 \ldots \times 100 &=\phantom{0000}42,34787878 \ldots\\[-1em]\cline{1-2}
\text{çıkararak, }42.34\dot{7}\dot{8} \times 9900 &= 423478-4234 &= 419244\\
\therefore 42.34\dot{7}\dot{8}&=\dfrac{419244}{9900} =\dfrac{34937}{825} = 42\dfrac{287}{825}
\end{align*}
\end{centerpage}
\end{small}
$\therefore$ istenen adi kesirler sırasıyla $0.\dot{3} = \dfrac{1}{3},\  0.\dot{2}\dot{4} = \dfrac{8}{33},\  42.34\dot{7}\dot{8} = 42 \dfrac{287}{825}$'tir.

