(1 + y)^{5} = 1 + 5y +10y^{2} + 10y^{3} + 5y^{4} + y^{5} \text{ (Cevap)}
Binom teoremini kullanarak şunu elde ederiz: (1 + y)^{5}
= \binom{5}{0} y^{0} + \binom{5}{1} y^{1} + \binom{5}{2} y^{2} + \binom{5}{3} y^{3} + \binom{5}{4} y^{4} + \binom{5}{5} y^{5}
= 1.1 + \frac{5}{1} y + \frac{5.4}{1.2} y^{2} + \frac{5.4.3}{1.2.3} y^{3} + \frac{5.4.3.2}{1.2.3.4} y^{4} + 1.y^{5}
= 1 + 5y + 10y^{2} + 10y^{3} + 5y^{4} + y^{5} \text{ (Cevap)}
(1 + y)^{5} ifadesinin açılımını kullanarak:
(1) (1 - y)^{5} = \{1 + (-y)\}^{5}
= 1 + 5(-y) + 10(-y)^{2} + 10(-y)^{3} + 5(-y)^{4} + (-y)^{5}
= 1 - 5y + 10y^{2} - 10y^{3} + 5y^{4} - y^{5} \text{ (Cevap)}

